  "displayTitle": "<span class=\"mw-page-title-main\">Dreadstone</span>",
  "html": "<div class=\"mw-content-ltr mw-parser-output\"><p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p>\n\n<p class=\"mw-empty-elt\"></p><p><i>Exclusive to:</i>  <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\"><img alt=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together icon.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png/32px-Don%27t_Starve_Together_icon.png?3bc208\" width=\"32\" height=\"35\"></a><br>\n</p>\n\n<p><b>Dreadstone</b> is an item exclusive to <i><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Don%27t_Starve_Together\" title=\"Don&#x27;t Starve Together\">Don&#x27;t Starve Together</a></i>. Dreadstone is primarily obtained by destroying the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Cracked_Pillar\" title=\"Cracked Pillar\">Cracked Pillars</a> that bind the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Nightmare_Werepig\" title=\"Nightmare Werepig\">Nightmare Werepig</a>. After mining away the outer <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Marble\" title=\"Marble\">Marble</a> layer, the pillars are indestructible and can only be destroyed by the Nightmare Werepig&#x27;s slam attack, which it only uses after losing enough HP. The Dreadstone can also be mined from <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Outcrop\" title=\"Dreadstone Outcrop\">Dreadstone Outcrop</a>.\n</p><p>With the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shadow_Courtier\" class=\"mw-redirect\" title=\"Shadow Courtier\">Shadow Courtier</a> skill, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Wilson\" title=\"Wilson\">Wilson</a> can transmute 3 Pure Horrors into 1 Dreadstone, as well as transmute 1 Dreadstone back into 2 Pure Horrors.\n</p><p>Along with <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror\" title=\"Pure Horror\">Pure Horror</a>, Dreadstone is used to craft <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Helm\" title=\"Dreadstone Helm\">Dreadstone Helm</a>, <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Armor\" title=\"Dreadstone Armor\">Dreadstone Armor</a> and <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Wall\" title=\"Dreadstone Wall\">Dreadstone Wall</a>. 5 Dreadstones can be offered to the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Beckoning_Hand\" title=\"Beckoning Hand\">Beckoning Hand</a> after defeating the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Ancient_Fuelweaver\" title=\"Ancient Fuelweaver\">Ancient Fuelweaver</a> to summon <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Charlie\" title=\"Charlie\">Charlie</a> and permanently activate the <a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Shadow_Rift\" title=\"Shadow Rift\">Shadow Rift</a>.\n</p>\n<h2><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Usage\"><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Icon_Tools\" title=\"Icon Tools\"><img alt=\"Icon Tools.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Icon_Tools.png/32px-Icon_Tools.png?f672d4\" width=\"32\" height=\"39\"></a> Usage</span></h2>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone\" title=\"Dreadstone\"><img alt=\"Dreadstone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dreadstone.png?560b78\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>6</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror\" title=\"Pure Horror\"><img alt=\"Pure Horror.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Horror.png?80afc3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint_(rare)\" title=\"Blueprint (rare)\"><img alt=\"Blueprint (rare).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint_%28rare%29.png/42px-Blueprint_%28rare%29.png?a2cbec\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Armor\" title=\"Dreadstone Armor\"><img alt=\"Dreadstone Armor.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dreadstone_Armor.png?804838\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone\" title=\"Dreadstone\"><img alt=\"Dreadstone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dreadstone.png?560b78\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Pure_Horror\" title=\"Pure Horror\"><img alt=\"Pure Horror.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Pure_Horror.png?80afc3\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint_(rare)\" title=\"Blueprint (rare)\"><img alt=\"Blueprint (rare).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint_%28rare%29.png/42px-Blueprint_%28rare%29.png?a2cbec\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Helm\" title=\"Dreadstone Helm\"><img alt=\"Dreadstone Helm.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dreadstone_Helm.png?da4dc0\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td></tr></tbody></table>\n<table><tbody><tr><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone\" title=\"Dreadstone\"><img alt=\"Dreadstone.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dreadstone.png?560b78\" width=\"64\" height=\"64\"></a></div></div></td><td><p>×<b>4</b></p></td><td><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Blueprint_(rare)\" title=\"Blueprint (rare)\"><img alt=\"Blueprint (rare).png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Blueprint_%28rare%29.png/42px-Blueprint_%28rare%29.png?a2cbec\" width=\"42\" height=\"42\"></a></td><td><div class=\"icon-frame\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/Dreadstone_Wall\" title=\"Dreadstone Wall\"><img alt=\"Dreadstone Wall.png\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dread