ass=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Dreadstone_Old.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Beta Dreadstone Icon\"><img alt=\"Beta Dreadstone Icon\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/Dreadstone_Old.png?de08c6\" width=\"120\" height=\"120\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Beta Dreadstone Icon</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n\t\t<li class=\"gallerybox\"><div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"thumb\"><div><a href=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/wiki/File:Dreadstone_Old_Dropped.png\" class=\"image\" title=\"Beta Dreadstone\"><img alt=\"Beta Dreadstone\" src=\"https://dontstarve.wiki.gg/images/thumb/Dreadstone_Old_Dropped.png/120px-Dreadstone_Old_Dropped.png?86b9a9\" width=\"120\" height=\"86\"></a></div></div>\n\t\t\t<div class=\"gallerytext\">Beta Dreadstone</div>\n\t\t</div></li>\n</ul>\n\n\n\n\n\n</div>",
